-- MOVES-DFG hires Goldman executives to leveraged loan platform
-- 
-- Tue Dec 16, 2014 10:24AM EST
-- None



Dec 16 (Reuters) - Asset management firm DFG Investment Advisers Inc said Roberta Goss and Timothy Milton from Goldman Sachs <GS.N> have joined the company as senior members of its leveraged loan platform.

Goss, who has more than 20 years of investment experience, was the managing director and co-head of Goldman's high-yield and bank loan businesses.